content.data: Now for something different, we will be creating a Corbel or Counter Top Support from a Base Object. See picture below. A "Base Object" is a base cabinet that has been set to a default cabinet and then had all the parts deleted. It is used to create your own objects from scratch.
Very Important! Preliminary Setup for the Fifth Exercises
Before starting this exercise it is important to setup a material schedule that is using a board stock material for the part called board.
